Change Log
==========

Feature Requests
----------------
- add user documentation
- fully unit tested: Functional tests start a daemon and send interrupt signals
- add system manager (isolates a process)
- refactor cron manager
- refactor parallel manager
- boot script (/etc/init.d/phptaskdaemon)
- cron restart script (for restarting after critical errors)

Version 2.1
-----------
+ Implement Daemon\Ipc types
    + Database
+ Implement Task\Manager\Trigger types
    + Cron
    + Gearman
+ Implement Task\Manager\Process types
    + Child
    + Parallel
- Load tasks components using the configuration file

Version 2.0
-----------
- add database support
- add exception handling
+ Add Daemon\Config component
+ Add Task\Job\Data component
+ Refactor Manager Trigger Component
+ Support for multiple IPC types
+ Implement Daemon\Ipc types
    + None
    + SharedMemory
+ Create Manager Trigger Component
+ Implement Task\Manager\Trigger types
    + Interval
+ Create Manager Process Component
+ Implement Task\Manager\Process types
    + Same
+ Refactor manager to use processes & triggers


Verison 0.6
